To install, you must already have an IMAP server set up. You will also need a webserver with mysql and php with the php-imap library.

   1. Copy config.php.example to config.php and edit values to suit your server
   2. Run the structure.sql file on your database.

For more information, please see http://freedomdreams.co.uk/wiki/AGPLMail
